"headword":"sustainable development"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：An optimist sees an opportunity in any calamity. （乐观者在任何"},{"type":"text","text":"灾难中都能看到机会。）"}]},{"number":1804,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"B：Yeah, they always look on the bright side. （是的，他们总是看"},{"type":"text","text":"到好的一面。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Every year, the South has floods. It is an act of God. （南方每年"},{"type":"text","text":"都发洪水，这是天灾。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Do you really think so? （你真的这么认为吗？）"}]}]}